title: IAA Tonight | Ranking the Top 10 WR's for the 2022 NFL Season
description: Brandon Marshall, Omar Kelly, Auntie Chantel Tremitiere, and Ashley Nicole Moss take a deep dive into ranking the top 10 wide receivers heading into the 2022 season. Of course, no one could come to an agreement on who's the best. Plus, who's career would you rather have: 10x NBA All-Star Carmelo Anthony or 4x NBA Champion and Finals MVP Andre Iguodala?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Brandon Marshall, Omar Kelly, Auntie Chantel Tremitiere, Ashley Nicole)
